reviews.reviewbody:
This book contains a large collection of songs, and piano solo and duet music. The songs are largely children's and folk songs. The piano music is an excellent selection of major and minor composers and is suitable for the first two grades.

It's quite unfortunate that the "Digitized by Microsoft" watermark obscures both musical notation and text in numerous instances. I had to print out the offending pages, add acrylic paint to white-out to get a suitable colour, white-out the pages and recopy the information by hand in order to make it readable. I would otherwise have given this a four-star rating.
